==============================================================================
                   Release of version 0.02 of Perl6::Rules
==============================================================================


Perl6/Rules version 0.01
=========================

This module prototypes the Perl 6 pattern matching and grammar syntax.


INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Attribute::Handlers
  Filter::Simple


